formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
This certificate is issued subject to following Notes:
Notes :
1)Form- 3 Annexure has been reproduced as submitted by client.
2) So far Encumbrance status is concerned, we are neither technically nor legally entitled to certify such charge. This legally falls exclusively under the Jurisdiction of an Advocate. 
3) We are Chartered Accountants and are entitled to certify the financial data as per book of accounts. We are neither technically nor educationally qualified to certify the Architect & Engineer work whether it seems in coherence with expenditure incurred. So we have certified only financial data which is our Jurisdiction  
(4) As matter of fact, there are 96 flats in the project. Also, there are 96 flats as per approved plan. 
(i) There are 96 flats in the projects.
(ii) There are 96 flats passed as per Approved plan. 
(ii) SMC has issued BUC (Building use permission) of 96 flats. But by mistake in Form-3(Annexure) booking details, the nos. of flats shown as 89 flats. So this is apparent computer date entry operator mistake. As a matter of facts, there are 96 flats only.
